<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Your Account Has Been Created</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .password-box {
            background: #fff;
            border: 2px solid #28a745;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .password {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #28a745;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        .warning {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #6c757d;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Blog Platform</h1>
        <p>Your account has been successfully created</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{fullName}},</h2>
        
        <p>Your administrator has created an account for you on our blog platform. Below are your login credentials:</p>
        
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
        <p><strong>Account:</strong> {{account}}</p>
        
        <div class="password-box">
            <p><strong>Your Temporary Password:</strong></p>
            <div class="password">{{password}}</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="warning">
            <strong>⚠️ Important Security Notice:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>This is a temporary password generated by the system</li>
                <li>Please change your password immediately after your first login</li>
                <li>Do not share this password with anyone</li>
                <li>This email contains sensitive information - please delete it after use</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p>You can now login to your account using the credentials above.</p>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact your administrator.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The Blog Platform Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent automatically. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>© 2024 Blog Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
